    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring dependable performance on the road. While there are a few minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. You can expect a car that is ready for daily use with no immediate mechanical concerns.",
