    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, there are no major mechanical issues or significant cosmetic defects. You can expect a solid, comfortable ride from a car that still has plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 33500.0,
