    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a handy parts car? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention to get back to its best, it offers a great foundation for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for an affordable entry into their next automotive challenge.",
